#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_dreamweb.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by Creative Reality (founded by Neil Dodwell and David Dew) and published by Empire Interactive in 1994. You are Ryan, an ordinary man plagued by nightmares about the Dreamweb — a mystical barrier protecting reality from chaos. Seven corrupt guardians have infiltrated the waking world, and Ryan must stop them. The game features a unique top-down perspective and explores mature, dark themes."
msgstr "由Creative Reality开发(由尼尔·多德威尔和大卫·杜(英语:David Dew)),1994年由Empire Interactive出版. 你是瑞安,一个被梦网的噩梦困扰的普通人——一个神秘的屏障,保护现实免于混乱. 七个腐败的守护者潜入了醒悟世界,瑞安必须阻止他们. 游戏以独特的自上而下视角为特色,探索成熟,黑暗的主题."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_chex_quest.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by Digital Cafe on a $500,000 budget for the WatersMolitor promotion agency, hired by Ralston Foods. Chex Quest shipped with 5.7 million boxes of Rice Chex, Wheat Chex, and Corn Chex in 1996–1997. Digital Cafe licensed the DOOM engine cheaply from id Software because Quake had already been released and id considered DOOM out of the spotlight."
msgstr "由Digital Cafe根据沃特斯莫利托推广机构50万美元的预算开发,由拉尔斯顿食品公司雇用. Chex Quest在1996-1997年以570万箱大米Chex,小麦Chex和玉米Chex装运. Digital Cafe从id Software便宜地许可了DOOM引擎,因为Quake已经发布,id认为DOOM脱离了聚光灯."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_fotaq.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by Interactive Binary Illusions, an Australian partnership between John Passfield and Steve Stamatiadis, established in 1993. Development spanned four years (1991–1995), initially built on the Amiga 500 using the AMOS programming language. The MS-DOS port was rewritten from scratch in C by Tony Ball. The game follows pilot Joe King as he navigates the Amazon after a plane crash, encountering a mad scientist, dinosaur hybrids, and Amazonian warriors."
msgstr "由交互式二进制幻象公司(Interactive Binary Illusions)开发,是约翰·帕斯菲尔德和史蒂夫·斯塔马蒂亚迪斯(Steve Stamatiadis)于1993年建立的一个澳大利亚伙伴关系. 开发历时4年(1991-1995年),最初采用AMOS编程语言在Amiga 500的基础上发展. MS-DOS端口在C中由托尼·鲍尔(Tony Ball)从零开始重写. 游戏跟随飞行员乔·金(Joe King)在飞机坠毁后航行亚马逊时,遭遇了一位疯狂科学家,恐龙杂交,亚马逊勇士."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_soltys.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by Polish studio LK Avalon and released on May 23, 1995 for MS-DOS. The title \"Soltys\" means \"Mayor\" (village head) in Polish. The player must convince Leon, the fiance of the mayor's daughter, to return to the wedding he has fled — leading to a bizarre journey through a surreal world full of folklore-based humor and creative puzzles."
msgstr "由波兰工作室LK Avalon开发,于1995年5月23日为MS-DOS发行. 标题\"Soltys\"在波兰语中意为\"市长\"(村长). 玩家必须说服市长女儿的未婚夫莱昂回到他所逃离的婚礼上——导致一个充满民俗幽默和创意谜题的超现实世界的奇异旅程."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by Spanish studio Alcachofa Soft and released in 1996. British real estate agent John Hacker travels to Transylvania and gets entangled in Count Drascula's plot to reanimate Frankenstein and take over the world. The name is a parody of Bram Stoker's Dracula, and the game is packed with references to horror movies, pop culture, and absurdist comedy."
msgstr "由西班牙工作室Alcachofa Soft开发,1996年发行. 英国房地产经纪人约翰·哈克(John Hacker)前往特兰西瓦尼亚,并陷入德拉斯库拉伯爵重新激活弗兰肯斯坦并占领世界的阴谋中. 这个名字是布拉姆·斯托克的\"德古拉\"(英语:Bram Stoker's Dracula)的讽刺作品,游戏中充满了恐怖电影,流行文化,以及荒谬主义喜剧的参考."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom_shareware.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Developed by id Software (John Carmack, John Romero, Sandy Petersen) and released on December 10, 1993, DOOM was uploaded to an FTP server at the University of Wisconsin and spread like wildfire across the early internet. As a lone space marine, fight your way through military bases overrun by hellspawn using an arsenal that includes the iconic shotgun, chaingun, and rocket launcher."
msgstr "由id Software(英语:John Carmack, John Romero, Sandy Petersen)开发,1993年12月10日发布,DOOM上传至威斯康辛大学的FTP服务器,并像野火一样传播到早期的互联网上. 作为一个孤独的太空海军陆战队, 利用一个包括标志性猎枪、链枪和火箭发射器的军火库, 通过被地狱喷泉攻破的军事基地战斗。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_fotaq.html.heex:87
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Development spanned four years and was originally built on the Amiga 500 using the AMOS programming language. The MS-DOS port was completely rewritten from scratch in C."
msgstr "开发历时四年,最初是使用AMOS编程语言在Amiga 500的基础上建设的. MS-DOS端口在C中从零开始完全重写."

