#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Dreamweb (1994) is a dark cyberpunk top-down adventure by Creative Reality — a disturbing journey through the Dreamweb, a mystical barrier protecting reality, heavily inspired by Blade Runner."
msgstr "Dreamweb (1994年)是\"创造现实\"(Creative Reality)的一场黑暗的网络朋克自上而下的冒险——通过Dreamweb的令人不安的旅程,是保护现实的神秘屏障,深受\"刀锋奔跑者\"的启发."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_dreamweb.html.heex:87
