#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife_uplink.html.heex:122
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2_shareware.html.heex:130
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D"
msgstr "沃尔芬斯坦3D"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:150
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:113
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:179
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:109
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D (Arcade)"
msgstr "沃尔芬施泰因3D(拱廊)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:84
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:94
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D used raycasting (not true 3D) — all walls are the same height and floors are flat. The 3D effect is an optical illusion."
msgstr "沃尔芬施泰因3D用光播音(并非真实的3D)——所有墙壁高度相同,地板平整. 3D效应是一种光学幻觉."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:35
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D: Escape from Castle"
msgstr "沃尔芬斯坦3D:逃离城堡"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:116
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Xash3D-FWGS"
msgstr "Xash3D-FWGS 系统"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_lure.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "You play Diermot, a peasant who must free the village of Turnvale from the sorceress Selena and her army of Skorl. The game reached #1 on the British Gallup charts at the beginning of July 1992 and remained in the Top 20 for most of the year. Released as freeware on April 1, 2003. Runs on ScummVM compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "你扮演Diermot,一个农民 他必须释放Turnvale村 从女巫Selena和她的军队Skorl。 游戏于1992年7月初在英国盖洛普海图上达到#1,并在当年的大部分时间里一直保持在前20名. 2003年4月1日作为免费软件发布. 运行在编译到 Web Assembly 的 ScummVM 上 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "and type:"
msgstr "和类型 :"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom_shareware.html.heex:100
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "id Software estimated only 1% of shareware downloaders bought the full game — yet this generated $100,000 per day in initial revenue, selling in one day what Wolfenstein 3D had sold in one month."
msgstr "id Software估计只有1%的共享软件下载者购买了完整的游戏——然而这每天获得了10万美元的初始收入,一天内卖出了Wolfenstein 3D在一个月里已经售出的东西."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:88
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "id Software purchased the Wolfenstein trademark for just $5,000 in mid-April 1992, weeks before the game launched."
msgstr "id Software在1992年4月中旬,即游戏推出前几周,仅以5000美元的价格购买了Wolfenstein商标."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:88
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2_shareware.html.heex:103
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "id Software released the Quake II source code under GPL in 2001, leading to dozens of enhanced source ports including Yamagi Quake II used here."
msgstr "id Software于2001年在GPL下发布了Quake II源代码,导致数十个增强源端口,包括此处使用的Yamagi Quake II."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:96
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "id Software released the full Wolfenstein 3D source code in 1995, spawning decades of source ports and mods."
msgstr "id Software于1995年发布了完整的Wolfenstein 3D源代码,催生了几十年的源端口和mods."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 32 deathmatch arenas (BSD license)"
msgstr "- 32个死亡竞技场(BSD许可证)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:39
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 32 deathmatch-focused arena maps. BSD license."
msgstr "——32幅死赛重点竞技场地图. BSD许可证."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:60
